@startuml Storage Enforcement - File Upload Sequence Diagram
!theme default
title Storage Enforcement System - File Upload Request Flow

actor User
participant "File Upload\nEndpoint" as Endpoint
participant "StorageEnforcementService" as Service
participant "StorageEnforcementConfig\nRepository" as Repo
database "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB

User -> Endpoint: POST /api/upload\n{file, size}
activate Endpoint

Endpoint -> Endpoint: Extract organisation_id\nfrom JWT token

Endpoint -> Service: can_upload(\n  percent_used=78.5,\n  organisation_id='org-123'\n)
activate Service

Service -> Repo: get_config_for_organisation_or_default(\n  organisation_id='org-123'\n)
activate Repo

Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM storage_enforcement_configs\nWHERE organisation_id = 'org-123'\nAND is_system_default = FALSE
activate DB

alt Org-Specific Config Found
  DB -> Repo: Row {config}
  Repo -> Repo: Parse to StorageEnforcementConfig
else No Org Config
  deactivate DB
  Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM storage_enforcement_configs\nWHERE is_system_default = TRUE
  activate DB
  DB -> Repo: Row {system_default}
  Repo -> Repo: Parse to StorageEnforcementConfig
end

deactivate DB
Repo -> Service: StorageEnforcementConfig(\n  enforcement_type='soft',\n  hard_limit_percent=110,\n  actions_json={...},\n  ...\n)
deactivate Repo

Service -> Service: action = get_enforcement_action(\n  percent_used=78.5,\n  config\n)

Service -> Service: Lookup '50_to_80' range\nin actions_json

Service -> Service: action = {\n  'status': 'yellow',\n  'upload': 'allowed',\n  'notifications': 'weekly_reminder'\n}

Service -> Service: upload_status = 'allowed'

Service -> Endpoint: return (True, "")
deactivate Service

Endpoint -> Endpoint: Upload allowed!\nProcess file...

Endpoint -> User: 200 OK\n{file_id, upload_status}
deactivate Endpoint

note over User, DB
  **Configuration Resolution:**
  1. ✅ Organisation-specific config found
  2. Would fallback to system default if not found
  3. Would use internal defaults if neither found

  **Enforcement Decision:**
  - percent_used (78.5%) → '50_to_80' range
  - actions_json['50_to_80'] → { 'upload': 'allowed' }
  - Result: Upload permitted with no warning
end note

@enduml
